{"tid":107373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12歲女童疑遭75歲老父強姦被捕","createTime":"2017-02-04T12:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T14:50:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e53eaf9319b3b84a35130a6bd127b7c47be8603","tid":107373,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:25:45.000Z","msg":"西九龍揭發七旬父涉嫌強姦年幼女兒的倫常風化案！消息稱，案件發生於西九龍區一個「老夫少妻」的家庭，75歲老翁與妻子育有一名12歲女兒，該家庭有社工跟進。據了解，社工早前發現受害女童有異樣，遂帶她到區內一間公立醫院求醫，其後相信女童曾遭人性侵。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，警方昨晚7時許接獲女童的家人報案，調查後相信女童曾遭75歲父親強姦，探員將涉案父親拘捕，他涉嫌強姦罪被帶署通宵扣查，案件交西九龍總區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00001/1486204450225#sthash.WX6Z0G0V.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00001%2F1486204450225%23sthash.WX6Z0G0V.dpuf&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD17IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c6e6c52c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00001%2F1486204450225%23sthash.WX6Z0G0V.dpuf&h=1e8990cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00001/1486204450225#sthash.WX6Z0G0V.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"edcb6541bf3f3def67030e31610b3d63ce2ee587","tid":107373,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"捉條廢老去印度比人輪啦"},{"pid":"57f89d78b6a7664d0e652ee645eacc605d4fff89","tid":107373,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:33:53.000Z","msg":"75歲係咪成日食海天堂"},{"pid":"2f99c5c3767f3f073d8ec0f2f042e8c10b5eab93","tid":107373,"uid":82186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dc1b3c40906d13aa917d48aee635aa1cf23984","tid":107373,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0